article.description: — Storm Murphy had a career-high 28 points as Wofford defeated Western Carolina 91-78 on Saturday.
article.headline: Murphy's career-high 28 carry Wofford over Western Carolina
article.linkText: Murphy's career-high 28 carry Wofford over Western Carolina
article.story: SPARTANBURG, S.C. -- — Storm Murphy had a career-high 28 points as Wofford defeated Western Carolina 91-78 on Saturday. Tray Hollowell had 18 points for Wofford (9-4, 6-1 Southern Conference), which earned its fourth straight win. Morgan Safford added 15 points. Sam Godwin had three blocks with eight points. Matt Halvorsen had 19 points for the Catamounts (7-7, 0-5), who have now lost five straight games. Cory Hightower added 15 points. Marcus Thomas had 14 points and Xavier Cork 13. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com ------
